<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20794367">为什么说将「直升机」称为「直升飞机」是错误的？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="498207" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">来自 @<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/skywalkerhan" class="internal">skywalkerhan</a> 答《<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/20271699/answer/14567332" class="internal">直升机坠地是否一定会爆炸？</a>》——<br><blockquote>纠正一下，没有直升飞机这个词！是直升机！</blockquote></div>


</div>
